Beyonce is giving us a look at her adorable twins in this new picture. Queen B and JAY-Z  turned Europe On The Run II World Tour into a family vacation. The music icons went for the concert bringing along their 6-year-old daughter, Blue Ivy, and their 1-year-old twins, son Sir and daughter Rumi. The Carters family is back in the states, Beyonce the proud mom shared an enormous collection of vacation photos to her website, including a snapshot of herself holding Sir and Rumi in her arms. Beyonce and her twins, Photo; Beyonce.com She also posted another photo of Rumi, held by her dad while they stood at the back of an enormous yacht, as they traveled through idyllic European waters. JAY Z and Rumi